        <h1>What Is BlackJack?</B> </h1>
        BlackJack is a card game the objective of whcih to be dealt cards having a higher count than those of the dealer up to but not exceeding 21.<br>
        <hr>    
     
        <B>Objective:</B><br>
        The objective of black jack is to beat the house(aka the dealer). <br>
        To do this you must use your cards to get close to 21 but never over 21. <br>
        If you go over 21 GAME OVER!!!
        <br>
       
        <B>How To Play:</B>
            <ol>
            <li>Place Your Bet</li>
            <li> 2 Cards Are Dealt To Each Player Face Up </li>
            <li> Evaluate Your Hand</li>
                <li> The Dealer Will Be Revealed At This Time </li>
            <li> Depending On The Total Of Your Cards You May Choose:</li>
                <ul>
                <li> <B>Stand Or Stay:</B>(take no additonal Cards)</li>
                <li> <B>Hit:</B>(Recieve Addittional Cards)</li>
                <li> <B>Double Down:</B>( Double Your Original Bet)</li>
                <li> <B>Split:</B> (Add An Additional Bet To Turn 2 Cards Of The Same Value Into 2 Seperate Hands)
                <li> <B>BlackJack:</B>(If Your First 2 Cards Are An Ace And A 10-Value Card You've Got A BlackJack)</li>
                    <ul>
                        <li> You Can Relax And Collect 150% Of Your Original Bet (3:2)</li>
                    </ul>
                </ul>
            <li> If You Have the Lowest Deck You loose Your Bet</li>
            <li> If You Were The Second To Last You Have A Push</li>
            <li> If You Won You Take The Losers Bets</li>
            <img scr="OneDrive-Personal/Documents/Pictures/BadBust.jpg" alt="">
            </ol>  
        <B>Rules Of Blackjack:</B>
            <ol>
                <li>2-10 cards conut are the value on the card</li>
                <li>Face Cards(Joker, Queen, King) Count as 10</li>
                <li>Ace counts as either 1 or 11( which ever helps your hand)</li>
            </ol>
       
        <B>Tips:</B>
        <ol>
            <li> Start Small</li>
            <li>Check The dealer's Up Card</li>
            <li>GOOD LUCK!!!</li>
        </ol>
     
